293
00:16:47,020 --> 00:16:47,980
We can dig a tunnel

294
00:16:48,180 --> 00:16:49,420
to pimpon tree

295
00:16:49,740 --> 00:16:50,820
and come out

296
00:16:51,100 --> 00:16:52,420
when the four boa constrictors

297
00:16:52,660 --> 00:16:53,700
leave to absorb spirits of heaven and earth.

298
00:16:53,940 --> 00:16:55,900
And then we leave from the tunnel after we get pimpon fruit.

299
00:16:56,220 --> 00:16:57,980
In that way, no one will even know about it.

300
00:16:59,740 --> 00:17:01,420
You are so smart.

301
00:17:02,220 --> 00:17:03,700
Let's go dig the tunnel today

302
00:17:03,700 --> 00:17:05,060
and start to take action tomorrow.

303
00:17:05,820 --> 00:17:06,420
Cool.

304
00:17:15,100 --> 00:17:16,540
Is it done?

305
00:17:16,860 --> 00:17:17,540
Yes.

306
00:17:20,980 --> 00:17:22,460
Do you think we should go down and have a check?

307
00:17:22,740 --> 00:17:24,820
Can the tunnel really connect to pimpon tree?

308
00:17:24,820 --> 00:17:25,620
It's not necessary.

309
00:17:26,020 --> 00:17:28,100
My Locating Magic can't go wrong.

310
00:17:28,380 --> 00:17:28,780
Let's go back.

311
00:17:29,020 --> 00:17:30,260
We'll come here at this time tomorrow.

312
00:17:30,940 --> 00:17:31,940
Wait.

313
00:17:32,980 --> 00:17:34,140
I think you should find something

314
00:17:34,340 --> 00:17:35,220
to cover the hole.

315
00:17:35,580 --> 00:17:36,580
It will be obvious

316
00:17:36,820 --> 00:17:38,460
when the day breaks.

317
00:17:39,460 --> 00:17:40,420
You're right.

318
00:17:46,100 --> 00:17:46,380
Done.

319
00:17:46,380 --> 00:17:46,900
Let's go.

320
00:17:47,020 --> 00:17:47,460
Okay.

321
00:18:18,340 --> 00:18:20,020
Master, you're back.

322
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:27,380
Master,

323
00:18:28,620 --> 00:18:30,580
I've heated the soup for you.

324
00:18:31,100 --> 00:18:31,820
Please drink it while it's hot.

325
00:18:33,060 --> 00:18:34,260
You don't need to

326
00:18:35,260 --> 00:18:36,620
take care of such trivial matters.

327
00:18:37,620 --> 00:18:40,460
Looking after master

328
00:18:40,820 --> 00:18:43,620
is my way of repaying your favors.

329
00:18:46,740 --> 00:18:47,940
It won't consume much of my cultivation

330
00:18:48,340 --> 00:18:49,660
to suppress Qiushui Toxin in you.

331
00:18:50,300 --> 00:18:51,500
You don't have to worry about it.

332
00:18:52,660 --> 00:18:54,620
Master, you have been so good to me.

333
00:18:55,460 --> 00:18:58,300
For my happiness,

334
00:18:58,780 --> 00:19:00,180
you helped me escape the wedding

335
00:19:00,420 --> 00:19:01,620
at the risk of sacrificing your own reputation.

336
00:19:01,980 --> 00:19:05,180
I'm very grateful for all that you've done for me.

337
00:19:06,220 --> 00:19:08,300
As immortals, we have endless time in the world.

338
00:19:08,860 --> 00:19:11,460
Don't be obsessed with things in the past.

339
00:19:12,380 --> 00:19:14,340
But what have happened

340
00:19:14,540 --> 00:19:15,540
is still so vivid to me.

341
00:19:17,980 --> 00:19:20,260
Master, you come to Fanyin Valley once in ten years.

342
00:19:21,060 --> 00:19:22,340
When you are not around,

343
00:19:23,180 --> 00:19:25,380
Fanyin Valley is just

344
00:19:25,660 --> 00:19:28,300
a silent place for cultivation for me,

345
00:19:28,580 --> 00:19:29,740
with no enjoyment at all.

346
00:19:31,580 --> 00:19:33,220
Only when master is around,

347
00:19:34,300 --> 00:19:36,900
can this place be lively again.

348
00:19:38,020 --> 00:19:40,420
I hope master can stay here longer.

349
00:19:41,620 --> 00:19:42,420
So that

350
00:19:42,700 --> 00:19:46,100
I can savor it in the following ten years.

351
00:19:47,220 --> 00:19:47,820
This time,

352
00:19:48,700 --> 00:19:50,700
I will try my best to cure Qiushui Cold Toxin in you.

353
00:19:51,500 --> 00:19:52,980
Since you are not willing to go back to the world of the demons,

354
00:19:53,180 --> 00:19:54,300
you can go

355
00:19:54,980 --> 00:19:56,220
wherever you like

