359
00:20:04,700 --> 00:20:07,460
It was me who insisted on leaving.

360
00:20:07,740 --> 00:20:08,500
Now

361
00:20:09,460 --> 00:20:11,980
I'm too shamed to ask for any title.

362
00:20:12,940 --> 00:20:14,660
All I want is an opportunity

363
00:20:14,940 --> 00:20:16,060
