365
00:20:21,420 --> 00:20:23,260
You don't need to stay by my side.

366
00:20:24,380 --> 00:20:25,460
Is there someone

367
00:20:26,580 --> 00:20:29,820
by your side already?

368
00:20:30,820 --> 00:20:31,580
Or

369
00:20:32,900 --> 00:20:34,700
is there someone on your mind already?

370
00:20:36,740 --> 00:20:37,340
Is it...

371
00:20:38,340 --> 00:20:39,820
Is it Princess Jiuge?

372
00:20:44,180 --> 00:20:44,740
It's late.

373
00:20:45,620 --> 00:20:46,940
Go back and sleep.

374
00:20:48,900 --> 00:20:49,620
Okay.

375
00:21:25,420 --> 00:21:25,940
All right.

376
00:21:26,260 --> 00:21:28,140
I'll go down first since there's no one around.

377
00:21:28,860 --> 00:21:29,420
What's wrong?

378
00:21:29,420 --> 00:21:30,740
I think I should go check first, just in case.

379
00:21:31,020 --> 00:21:31,900
Wait for me.

380
00:21:32,700 --> 00:21:34,060
Be careful.

381
00:22:00,340 --> 00:22:01,500
It's weird.

382
00:22:02,660 --> 00:22:04,660
I remember I only dug one tunnel.

383
00:22:04,860 --> 00:22:06,740
Why are there three sideways?

384
00:22:10,660 --> 00:22:12,260
It's halfway past the time.

385
00:22:12,500 --> 00:22:14,620
Why hasn't Yan Chiwu come back?

386
00:22:17,820 --> 00:22:19,940
Does he...

387
00:22:20,780 --> 00:22:22,500
Yan is a good person.

388
00:22:23,260 --> 00:22:24,980
But he used to be a demon lord

389
00:22:25,140 --> 00:22:26,540
who did many evil things.

390
00:22:27,620 --> 00:22:28,700
Is he so damned that he got eaten up

391
00:22:29,660 --> 00:22:31,220
by the boa constrictors?

392
00:22:44,580 --> 00:22:45,780
What the hell is this place?

393
00:22:46,060 --> 00:22:48,780
I'm supposed to come out from under pimpon tree.

394
00:22:49,900 --> 00:22:51,900
Did I dig in the wrong direction?

395
00:22:53,220 --> 00:22:53,980
Never mind.

396
00:22:54,580 --> 00:22:56,500
I'll see if pimpon tree is nearby?

397
00:23:09,420 --> 00:23:10,140
Why...

398
00:23:12,260 --> 00:23:13,620
why did Yan Chiwu dig three tunnels?

399
00:23:13,860 --> 00:23:15,420
We need only one.

400
00:23:17,020 --> 00:23:18,660
It's taking too long for him to check the way.

401
00:23:19,420 --> 00:23:21,420
Could he go the wrong way?

402
00:24:06,220 --> 00:24:08,220
Where on earth is this place?

403
00:24:16,940 --> 00:24:17,540
It's bad.

404
00:24:19,220 --> 00:24:20,460
Sign of a red moon.

405
00:24:20,980 --> 00:24:22,340
Evil spirits are going to come out.

406
00:24:23,260 --> 00:24:24,100
Am I walking into a forbidden area

407
00:24:24,140 --> 00:24:25,660
where evil spirits are bound?

408
00:24:32,700 --> 00:24:36,700
Why don't you even look at me in the eyes, Your Majesty?

409
00:24:37,980 --> 00:24:39,420
Am I not

410
00:24:40,620 --> 00:24:42,380
beautiful enough?

411
00:24:47,740 --> 00:24:48,540
Your Majesty.

412
00:24:49,300 --> 00:24:50,660
You come here only once in ten years.

413
00:24:51,740 --> 00:24:55,380
Do you know how hard and torturing it is

414
00:24:55,820 --> 00:24:57,700
expecting you?

415
00:24:58,900 --> 00:24:59,860
You Majesty.

416
00:25:00,340 --> 00:25:02,460
I'll get mad if you

417
00:25:03,700 --> 00:25:06,140
don't look at me.

418
00:25:06,460 --> 00:25:08,500
Your Majesty, you are dating a banshee here?

419
00:25:09,180 --> 00:25:10,260
What are you doing here?

420
00:25:16,740 --> 00:25:19,100
Your Majesty, you are the most unromantic man

421
00:25:19,380 --> 00:25:20,940
in the Eight Deserts and Six Directions.

422
00:25:21,460 --> 00:25:25,700
Why are you bringing two friends while dating me?

423
00:25:26,460 --> 00:25:29,740
Don't you know that I will be mad?

424
00:25:32,500 --> 00:25:35,700
Oh, His Majesty was talking to her, not me.

425
00:26:00,820 --> 00:26:02,580
Girl, you are so stubborn.

426
00:26:03,420 --> 00:26:05,580
Why don't you leave with your friend?

427
00:26:06,220 --> 00:26:07,220
Do you want to see me

428
00:26:08,060 --> 00:26:10,900
and His Majesty spend the night?

429
00:26:26,100 --> 00:26:26,940
Keep doing what you are doing.

430
00:26:27,260 --> 00:26:28,740
I don't mind watching from aside.

431
00:26:29,780 --> 00:26:31,620
You can tell.

432
00:26:32,380 --> 00:26:34,220
The flowing currents in both of your bodies

433
00:26:34,420 --> 00:26:35,820
are the result of

434
00:26:35,900 --> 00:26:37,180
confrontation between strong spirits.

435
00:26:37,580 --> 00:26:40,180
Foling Flower is the holly flower of Sky Kingdom.

436
00:26:40,820 --> 00:26:42,020
It must be summoned here

437
00:26:42,340 --> 00:26:43,620
by His Majesty

438
00:26:43,820 --> 00:26:45,060
for cleansing his breath.

439
00:26:46,260 --> 00:26:48,660
You seem intimate with each other,

440
00:26:49,300 --> 00:26:51,900
but you are actually having a tough fight in disguise.

441
00:26:52,940 --> 00:26:53,620
Who

442
00:26:53,980 --> 00:26:55,300
are you?

443
00:26:56,020 --> 00:26:57,540
Since you can see it,

444
00:26:58,100 --> 00:27:00,020
you should leave right now.

445
00:27:03,900 --> 00:27:05,700
Since you want to be a part of it,

446
00:27:06,020 --> 00:27:08,900
I will give you the satisfaction.

447
00:27:37,100 --> 00:27:38,260
You are just nobody.

448
00:27:38,700 --> 00:27:40,660
How dare you challenge me?

449
00:27:55,940 --> 00:27:58,380
In every move, mind should go earlier than hands.

450
00:27:58,940 --> 00:28:00,100
The sword has to be drawn by the mind.

451
00:28:00,540 --> 00:28:01,900
That's what it takes to win the battle.

452
00:29:19,420 --> 00:29:20,580
Watch closely.

453
00:30:14,780 --> 00:30:16,180
Ji Heng?

454
00:30:19,580 --> 00:30:20,540
Ji Heng.

455
00:30:22,260 --> 00:30:22,820
Why are you here alone

456
00:30:23,060 --> 00:30:24,420
in the middle of the night?

457
00:30:27,980 --> 00:30:28,900
You are crying.

458
00:30:29,620 --> 00:30:30,660
Did the ice face pick on you?

459
00:30:31,100 --> 00:30:31,900
I'll go confront him.

460
00:30:32,580 --> 00:30:33,660
It's none of his business.

461
00:30:34,460 --> 00:30:34,980
I...

462
00:30:36,100 --> 00:30:38,420
I came out for a walk and got lost.

463
00:30:39,260 --> 00:30:43,660
And I happened to see the sad
and beautiful lotus pool under moonlight.

464
00:30:44,020 --> 00:30:45,940
So I couldn't help being sentimental here.

465
00:30:46,940 --> 00:30:47,660
No wonder.

466
00:30:48,260 --> 00:30:49,300
Are you lost, too?

467
00:30:49,420 --> 00:30:50,740
I got lost too.

468
00:30:51,020 --> 00:30:52,900
Fanyin Valley is such a weird place.

469
00:30:54,500 --> 00:30:57,340
Let me escort you back.

470
00:30:59,780 --> 00:31:01,020
Thank you, Yan.

471
00:31:03,260 --> 00:31:04,340
What did you call me?

472
00:31:05,940 --> 00:31:07,100
Demon Lord

473
00:31:08,780 --> 00:31:09,580
Yan.

474
00:31:09,860 --> 00:31:11,340
No, no, no. Don't add Demon Lord.

475
00:31:11,460 --> 00:31:13,060
Just call me Yan. It sounds friendlier.

476
00:31:13,580 --> 00:31:15,940
I like you calling me Yan.

477
00:31:25,060 --> 00:31:26,020
It's over?

478
00:31:26,380 --> 00:31:27,060
Yes, it's over.

479
00:31:29,500 --> 00:31:30,340
Why are you here?

480
00:31:31,420 --> 00:31:33,060
Who's the banshee?

481
00:31:34,740 --> 00:31:35,380
Wait.

482
00:31:36,140 --> 00:31:38,180
You asked me why I was here?

483
00:31:40,380 --> 00:31:42,580
Did I sound like I was talking to myself?

484
00:31:43,780 --> 00:31:44,460
No.

485
00:31:44,660 --> 00:31:46,500
I thought you asked Ji Heng why she was here.

486
00:31:46,900 --> 00:31:48,380
So you were actually asking me.

487
00:31:49,940 --> 00:31:50,780
Of course.

488
00:31:57,420 --> 00:31:58,460
You haven't answered me yet.

489
00:31:59,540 --> 00:32:00,460
Why are you here?

490
00:32:01,180 --> 00:32:02,140
I...

491
00:32:02,700 --> 00:32:04,180
I'm supposed to be

492
00:32:04,180 --> 00:32:05,260
stealing pimpon fruit at this time.

493
00:32:05,500 --> 00:32:06,660
But impulsion ran over me.

494
00:32:06,940 --> 00:32:07,820
And the moment I drew pottery-made sword,

495
00:32:08,020 --> 00:32:10,100
I completely forgot what I was supposed to do.

496
00:32:10,420 --> 00:32:11,980
And I have no idea how much time is left for me.

497
00:32:12,740 --> 00:32:14,340
I've got things to do. I have to go now.

498
00:32:14,620 --> 00:32:16,220
Aren't you going to take me with you?

499
00:32:17,860 --> 00:32:18,780
Why would I do that?

500
00:32:19,620 --> 00:32:20,380
I'm hurt.

501
00:32:21,860 --> 00:32:23,460
Do you want to leave me here alone?

502
00:32:24,340 --> 00:32:25,140
Don't you think it's unsafe for me?

503
00:32:26,180 --> 00:32:26,940
No.

504
00:32:27,220 --> 00:32:28,180
Not at all.

505
00:32:34,580 --> 00:32:35,100
You...

506
00:32:35,700 --> 00:32:37,940
Looks like you don't feel safe leaving me here.

507
00:32:40,380 --> 00:32:41,660
I'm sorry that

508
00:32:41,900 --> 00:32:42,820
I fail to tell

509
00:32:43,020 --> 00:32:44,460
you're hurt,

510
00:32:44,660 --> 00:32:46,140
judging from your charming bearing now.

511
00:32:57,140 --> 00:32:58,100
Legend has it that since Your Majesty

512
00:32:58,140 --> 00:32:59,860
took the throne,

513
00:33:00,180 --> 00:33:02,100
