514
00:33:03,300 --> 00:33:05,700
How surprising it is to see you

515
00:33:05,700 --> 00:33:07,820
get hurt today.

516
00:33:09,100 --> 00:33:10,100
Have you had enough?

517
00:33:12,540 --> 00:33:14,340
The red blood is even mixed with goldenness.

518
00:33:15,180 --> 00:33:16,940
Your Majesty's blood is indeed different.

519
00:33:17,340 --> 00:33:18,580
I also heard that

520
00:33:18,780 --> 00:33:20,740
a cup of Your Majesty's blood,

521
00:33:21,100 --> 00:33:23,580
