526
00:33:37,140 --> 00:33:39,060
You have fooled me several times.

527
00:33:39,260 --> 00:33:40,860
Who knows if this is your camouflage trick or not?

528
00:33:41,060 --> 00:33:42,580
I'm no fool.

529
00:33:45,460 --> 00:33:48,700
You are a lot smarter than before.

530
00:33:49,260 --> 00:33:51,100
But didn't your master who taught you magic art

531
00:33:51,260 --> 00:33:53,220
tell you in your childhood that

532
00:33:53,740 --> 00:33:56,140
the camouflage with bleeding can only deceit a mortal,

533
00:33:56,540 --> 00:33:58,660
but not an immortal?

534
00:34:04,180 --> 00:34:05,700
The wound is real?

535
00:34:09,260 --> 00:34:09,860
But

536
00:34:10,660 --> 00:34:12,940
you are not like all the heroes I have met.

537
00:34:13,100 --> 00:34:14,220
Take my uncle for example.

538
00:34:14,860 --> 00:34:16,140
No matter how badly injured he was,

539
00:34:16,420 --> 00:34:17,500
