540
00:34:17,660 --> 00:34:18,980
to keep my aunt from knowing it.

541
00:34:19,380 --> 00:34:20,700
It's the first time I saw

542
00:34:20,740 --> 00:34:22,020
someone who had such an overreaction.

543
00:34:24,180 --> 00:34:27,140
Because I am weaker

544
00:34:27,700 --> 00:34:28,820
than those heroes you know.

545
00:34:32,260 --> 00:34:33,940
Am I exaggerating?

546
00:34:35,420 --> 00:34:36,100
Sorry.

547
00:35:18,100 --> 00:35:18,780
Thank you

548
00:35:19,100 --> 00:35:19,980
for escorting me back.

549
00:35:33,420 --> 00:35:34,260
I got lucky

550
00:35:34,500 --> 00:35:35,980
to run into Ji Heng while I was lost.

551
00:35:37,740 --> 00:35:38,180
Oh no.

552
00:35:38,380 --> 00:35:39,340
I forgot about Xiaojiu.

553
00:35:44,260 --> 00:35:44,940
What are you looking at?

554
00:35:46,180 --> 00:35:47,020
I'm thinking.

555
00:35:48,660 --> 00:35:49,340
Thinking about what?

556
00:35:50,460 --> 00:35:51,180
Thinking about you.

557
00:35:59,260 --> 00:36:01,860
Why did you come all the way to Jieyou Spring
in the middle of the night?

558
00:36:02,180 --> 00:36:03,660
Damn, I totally forgot it.

559
00:36:04,020 --> 00:36:04,820
Yan...

560
00:36:05,140 --> 00:36:05,860
I...

