00:36:06,380 --> 00:36:07,020
Oh,

562
00:36:07,500 --> 00:36:09,100
I've got something to do. Bye now.

563
00:36:09,900 --> 00:36:10,820
Leaving so soon?

564
00:36:11,780 --> 00:36:13,900
Is that your way of doing things in Qingqiu?

565
00:36:15,100 --> 00:36:16,260
Of course.

566
00:36:16,540 --> 00:36:18,100
I have my own business.

567
00:36:18,540 --> 00:36:20,300
And I've patched you up.

568
00:36:20,540 --> 00:36:22,260
Excuse me if there's nothing else.

569
00:36:27,260 --> 00:36:28,460
I forgot to tell you that

570
00:36:28,860 --> 00:36:30,700
Miao Luo's breaking in will trigger the shut-down,

571
00:36:31,020 --> 00:36:32,300
so she will be trapped here.

572
00:36:32,900 --> 00:36:33,980
Although she's put down,

573
00:36:34,340 --> 00:36:36,100
the shut-down won't go away

574
00:36:36,340 --> 00:36:37,260
until 24 hours later

575
00:36:37,580 --> 00:36:39,020
for making sure nothing goes wrong.

576
00:36:39,380 --> 00:36:40,100
I'm afraid

577
00:36:40,500 --> 00:36:42,020
you can't go out for now.

578
00:36:42,980 --> 00:36:44,660
24 hours.

579
00:36:46,620 --> 00:36:48,100
What's so urgent

580
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:50,860
that you have to go out now?

581
00:36:51,580 --> 00:36:52,460
I have...

582
00:36:53,660 --> 00:36:55,380
I have an appointment with Yan Chiwu.

583
00:36:56,820 --> 00:36:58,300
Stealing pimpon fruit

584
00:36:58,380 --> 00:36:59,260
is not something I can talk about proudly

585
00:36:59,460 --> 00:37:00,820
with others.

586
00:37:02,700 --> 00:37:05,060
I have an appointment with Yan.

587
00:37:09,340 --> 00:37:09,820
Your Majesty,

588
00:37:10,180 --> 00:37:11,860
do you think

589
00:37:12,060 --> 00:37:12,940
I patched you up well?

590
00:37:13,500 --> 00:37:14,780
Do you owe me once?

591
00:37:15,060 --> 00:37:16,260
Do you want to return the favor?

592
00:37:17,580 --> 00:37:18,420
It's just so-so.

593
00:37:19,500 --> 00:37:21,060
What do you want from me in return?

594
00:37:22,300 --> 00:37:23,180
It's very simple.

595
00:37:23,460 --> 00:37:24,820
Such a place

596
00:37:25,100 --> 00:37:26,860
can only trap low-level immortals

597
00:37:26,860 --> 00:37:28,460
like me.

598
00:37:28,900 --> 00:37:30,140
Those immortals with high cultivation

599
00:37:30,300 --> 00:37:32,060
like you

600
00:37:32,260 --> 00:37:33,700
can't be trapped.

601
00:37:34,060 --> 00:37:34,980
If Your Majesty

602
00:37:35,100 --> 00:37:38,180
can help me get out of here,

603
00:37:38,660 --> 00:37:41,540
I will forgive you for

604
00:37:41,620 --> 00:37:43,380
your not coming to rescue me for over half a year

605
00:37:43,700 --> 00:37:44,820
after leaving me in Fanyin Valley

606
00:37:44,900 --> 00:37:46,980
and your turning into a handkerchief

607
00:37:47,380 --> 00:37:48,380
to deceive me into forgiving you.

608
00:37:48,660 --> 00:37:49,460
What do you think?

609
00:37:49,900 --> 00:37:50,980
I think

610
00:37:57,620 --> 00:37:59,620
you are holding a grudge against me.

611
00:38:00,820 --> 00:38:02,340
I'm not.

612
00:38:03,660 --> 00:38:04,300
Of course,

613
00:38:04,900 --> 00:38:07,420
no one will offend me except you.

614
00:38:10,140 --> 00:38:10,900
What about Yan Chiwu?

615
00:38:11,500 --> 00:38:12,460
Yan.

616
00:38:13,020 --> 00:38:14,180
Well, he's very nice.

617
00:38:21,500 --> 00:38:22,540
So, Your Majesty,

618
00:38:22,900 --> 00:38:25,020
are you going to help me get out

619
00:38:25,220 --> 00:38:26,300
or not?

620
00:38:28,340 --> 00:38:30,220
Why would I help you get out?

621
00:38:31,020 --> 00:38:32,020
Because I helped you.

622
00:38:33,740 --> 00:38:35,580
I helped you at a crucial time.

623
00:38:35,780 --> 00:38:37,380
And you should help me once too.

624
00:38:37,620 --> 00:38:38,740
That's what we call fairness.

625
00:38:39,780 --> 00:38:41,740
I don't know how to get you out.

626
00:38:43,940 --> 00:38:45,700
No matter how important your appointment is,

627
00:38:45,940 --> 00:38:48,220
you have to wait until 24 hours later.

628
00:38:52,140 --> 00:38:53,100
Xiaojiu.

629
00:38:53,940 --> 00:38:55,100
Xiaojiu.

630
00:38:56,820 --> 00:38:57,660
Where is she?

631
00:39:02,300 --> 00:39:03,500
If I miss the chance tonight,

632
00:39:03,980 --> 00:39:06,060
I have to wait until the 15th of next lunar month.

633
00:39:06,140 --> 00:39:07,620
It's one more month to go.

634
00:39:11,140 --> 00:39:13,300
I dragged Yan into this.

635
00:39:13,700 --> 00:39:15,140
Now he couldn't find me.

636
00:39:15,220 --> 00:39:16,620
He must be very anxious.

637
00:39:22,460 --> 00:39:25,940
I didn't know that you are so worried about Yan.

638
00:39:26,140 --> 00:39:27,860
I'm afraid he won't help me steal pimpon fruit again

639
00:39:28,060 --> 00:39:30,580
next month.

640
00:39:34,500 --> 00:39:35,380
No.

641
00:39:36,060 --> 00:39:36,900
Nothing.

642
00:39:38,580 --> 00:39:39,820
So you planned to steal pimpon fruit

643
00:39:40,020 --> 00:39:42,460
with Yan Chiwu.

644
00:39:44,180 --> 00:39:45,060
No.

645
00:39:45,980 --> 00:39:47,060
I am the princess of Qingqiu.

646
00:39:47,340 --> 00:39:48,940
I won't do such a thing.

647
00:39:49,100 --> 00:39:50,300
No, you heard it wrong.

648
00:39:53,140 --> 00:39:54,660
Maybe I did hear it wrong.

649
00:39:58,620 --> 00:40:00,140
I'm feeling a bit dizzy.

650
00:40:00,860 --> 00:40:01,620
Come here.

651
00:40:02,700 --> 00:40:03,700
Lend me your shoulder.

652
00:40:05,020 --> 00:40:05,660
Your Majesty.

653
00:40:06,500 --> 00:40:08,220
You may feel uncomfortable leaning on me.

654
00:40:08,620 --> 00:40:10,220
I can conjure a pillow for you.

655
00:40:10,540 --> 00:40:12,540
I feel like I recall something.

656
00:40:13,020 --> 00:40:14,500
You said the 15th of next lunar month...

657
00:40:15,180 --> 00:40:15,700
Your Majesty,

658
00:40:15,900 --> 00:40:17,380
are you feeling comfortable now?

659
00:40:17,620 --> 00:40:20,380
I can lie down for you to lean on.

660
00:40:20,620 --> 00:40:22,700
Should I lie down with my face up

661
00:40:22,820 --> 00:40:24,860
or my back up?

662
00:40:25,660 --> 00:40:28,820
Do you feel better sitting or lying?

663
00:40:29,220 --> 00:40:29,740
If I lie down,

664
00:40:29,900 --> 00:40:31,060
it means both of us are lying.

665
00:40:31,860 --> 00:40:32,860
I think sitting is better.

666
00:40:34,340 --> 00:40:35,620
Okay.

667
00:40:44,060 --> 00:40:44,580
Xiaojiu.

668
00:40:47,900 --> 00:40:48,380
Xiaojiu.

669
00:40:55,700 --> 00:40:57,060
I lost too much blood earlier.

670
00:40:57,540 --> 00:40:58,580
My hands are cold.

671
00:40:58,820 --> 00:41:00,180
Do you mind

672
00:41:01,260 --> 00:41:02,900
warming me up a little?

673
00:41:04,100 --> 00:41:05,340
It's improper for men and women to have physical contact.

674
00:41:07,940 --> 00:41:08,700
Sure.

675
00:41:10,140 --> 00:41:10,660
I want to meet the empress of inseparable king birds

676
00:41:10,900 --> 00:41:13,220
in a few days.

677
00:41:13,540 --> 00:41:15,780
I'll ask her how to plant pimpon tree.

678
00:41:16,020 --> 00:41:17,460
Do you think I should...

679
00:41:17,820 --> 00:41:18,420
Well, I don't think

680
00:41:18,740 --> 00:41:20,180
it's improper for men and women to have physical contact.

681
00:41:20,380 --> 00:41:21,540
That's the most ridiculous thing

682
00:41:21,780 --> 00:41:22,780
moralists come up with

683
00:41:22,980 --> 00:41:23,900
since the creation of the universe.

684
00:41:24,340 --> 00:41:25,620
I'm not sure if my hands are warm enough

685
00:41:26,020 --> 00:41:27,700
for you, Your Majesty.

686
00:41:29,700 --> 00:41:30,620
Quick learner.

687
00:41:31,220 --> 00:41:32,100
I'm tired.

688
00:41:32,420 --> 00:41:33,700
I want to get some sleep.

689
00:41:34,220 --> 00:41:35,300
Suit yourself.

690
00:41:38,100 --> 00:41:38,900
You just stood there

691
00:41:39,020 --> 00:41:40,460
and watched the whole thing.

692
00:41:41,100 --> 00:41:42,820
You're so cheeky to say you're tired.

693
00:41:43,300 --> 00:41:45,740
I just fought a tough fight and I even have to serve you.

694
00:41:45,980 --> 00:41:47,180
I'm much more tired than you.

695
00:41:47,620 --> 00:41:49,860
I know what's in your head.

696
00:41:50,060 --> 00:41:51,580
You think all I did was standing there and watching.

697
00:41:53,620 --> 00:41:55,100
I was encouraging you

698
00:41:56,340 --> 00:41:58,020
very seriously.

699
00:42:00,220 --> 00:42:01,340
I will take you out

700
00:42:01,740 --> 00:42:02,940
after I have enough rest.

701
00:42:50,860 --> 00:42:52,220
I went this way earlier.

702
00:42:53,300 --> 00:42:54,820
Xiaojiu must have gone either of the two ways.

703
00:42:55,340 --> 00:42:56,740
What if she went alone to steal pimpon fruit

704
00:42:56,820 --> 00:42:58,580
and got eaten up by the four boa constrictors?

705
00:42:59,660 --> 00:43:00,620
I have to find her soon.

706
00:43:22,540 --> 00:43:25,820
There are always people out there
trying to seek protection from me.

707
00:43:26,940 --> 00:43:29,980
It's the first time I met someone

708
00:43:30,740 --> 00:43:33,620
who wants to protect me instead.

